snippet.title: Espana Games '92 gameplay (PC Game, 1992)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Espana Games '92, Dos PC game produced by Creative Materials in 1992 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/espana-games-92/1918/
This game is a sport simulation which will take you to Barcelona, Spain, in year 1992 and put you in shoes of a professional athlete competing for the gold medal in various sport disciplines.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
The Games: Summer Challenge - https://youtu.be/0Kl9lK9Zdk8
